ple we consider dark matter composed of\nultra-light axions, which in the classical limit ($\\hbar/m\\to 0$) is expected\nto manifest itself as collisionless cold dark matter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Jan 2018 19:00:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Apr 2018 19:16:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-02"}
