e model. Half of all clusters are predicted to form\nwithin the redshift range $5<z<2.3$, corresponding to ages of $10.8-12.5$~Gyr,\nin halos of masses $10^{11}-10^{12.5} M_{\\odot}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Jan 2018 19:03:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Jan 2018 05:01:33 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 24 Jul 2018 21:10:05 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 23 Aug 2018 04:23:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-24"}
