 in the\nproposed policies, the largest throughput region in the single-battery case is\ncontained within that of the dual-battery case.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Jan 2018 15:25:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Jan 2018 15:42:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 18 Dec 2018 11:54:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-19"}
