ow to\napproximate these local sets. We further see how in these approximations the\nlabels naturally encode distances to the boundary.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Jan 2018 15:46:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 May 2018 08:04:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-02"}
